&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Own the end-to-end delivery from kickoff to go-live through renewal, ensuring clarity on expectations, timeline, and services budget for all stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
